SUMMARY:Magnolia Flea Market
DTSTAMP:20260403T051342Z
DTSTART:20260509T100000Z
DESCRIPTION:Discover a curated mix of vintage finds\\\, local makers\\\, ha
	ndmade goods\\\, sweet treats\\\, coffee\\\, and food—plus a vintage wareh
